'''Portentous Goldwoven: Universal Matrix''' is a [[Mission Item]].

==Text==
<div align="center">{{Color|Keyword|Portentous Goldwoven: Universal Matrix}}</div>
<div align="center">At a feast where all the Titans were present, Zagreus disguised themself as an actor and delivered tricks,</div><br /><div align="center">They placed a {{Color|keyword|nobold=1|full goblet}} on the Scale of Justice, and attempted to weigh the huge volume of water.</div><br /><div align="center">But the goblet unintentionally fell, and was caught by a {{Color|keyword|nobold=1|dark, gray hand}}.</div><br /><div align="center">They tied a {{Color|keyword|nobold=1|golden butterfly}} to the Pillar of Stone, and attempted to stop the currents of love,</div><br /><div align="center">But the butterfly flapped its wings and took flight toward its {{Color|keyword|nobold=1|lover's}} embrace.</div><br /><div align="center">They tossed the {{Color|keyword|nobold=1|spear of Strife}} toward the Gate of Infinity, and attempted to ruin the alliance between states,</div><br /><div align="center">But the spear passed through the myriad passages and surprisingly returned to its {{Color|keyword|nobold=1|master}}'s hand.</div><br /><div align="center">The gods were enraged by Zagreus's insolence, and descended their wrath upon them.</div><br /><div align="center">Look, who's the one that ended up {{Color|keyword|nobold=1|without a penny to their name}}? It's the incorrigible {{Color|keyword|nobold=1|god of trickery}}.</div>

